node.text:
•

F.E.A.R= Finally, Exiting, Average, Reality
•

In order for us to tap into that next orbit of our lives, we have to leave the fear behind.
•

Fear keeps us average, and i’ll be honest.. You are Extrodinary in so many aspects of your life.
•

But you’ll never tap in because you’re choosing F.E.A.R
•

You’ve become accustomed to not living on your higher self.
•

If a eagle lived with chickens, he’d accept the fact that he couldn’t soar.
•

It’s time for you to soar, it’s time for you to over come F.E.A.R.
•

It’s Time for you to live the life you Want.
•

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW

While in the Safari, I was about to actually see a lioness stalk her prey & go in for the kill.
•

it took a few hours, she was patient, she studied & analyzed all her options & locked it.
•

There were over 100 zebra & another 60 Impala out there.
•

She didn’t try to get them all, she didn’t move emotionally because of her fear of missing out.
•

She locked in, was patient, got closer, didn’t get anxious. And when it was time to dominate her prey, she did.
•

Investing is the same way, there’s over 4000 stocks on the exchange, you can’t get them all.
•

So if your patient & know how to study, the land will reward you well.
•

To learn more about studying the game and becoming a financial predator, come join Trappers Anonymous.
•

node.text:
If you’re looking to exceed your own expectations of yourself, that comes with Pressure.
•

Pressure can get intense, it can cause impaired vision, discouragement, failure depression and the list goes on.
•

But for a chosen few, it will sharpen the attack, it will bring out the best in you.
•

It is in those moments the champion in you emerge.
•

Game 6, Chicago vs Utah Jazz. Bulls down 3 with 42 seconds on the clock. Not another Bulls player touches the ball.
•

M.J splits a double Team drives to the paint and gets a lay up. He comes down, Karl Malone gets the ball in the paint. M.J leaves his man and goes and steal the ball.
•

The ball bounces a few times, there’s a scramble on the floor, M.J comes up with the ball.
•

He doesn’t pass it, he keeps the ball in his hands, goes down court, put one of the hardest moves on Utah’s best defender and hits the game winning Jumper.
•

Pressure!
•

Not only to make the final shot, but mindset to understand the moment & not shrink but to let the moment mold you.
•

Pressure… it’s inevitable for those seeking to accomplish things everyone can’t do.
•

Pressure, comes with being able to withstand criticism. Everyone says M.J commutes a offensive foul when he pushed off.
•

Well, who walked away with the ring? M.J or the critics.
•

Pressure, once you understand that it goes hand and hand with success, you embrace it & it makes you unstoppable!
•

Building wealth for generations comes with Pressure.
•

Being the first millionaire in your family will come with pressure.
•

Being a father will come with Pressure!
•

Being a Blackman in America will come with Pressure.
•

It either makes you better, or it breaks you. There’s No In between.
•

Big Trap🏚⚖️🏚⚖️
